{"tid":370913,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"十一月第一次去泰國,仲要同屋企人去,希望咁多巴打俾D意見","createTime":"2017-08-23T10:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T06:05:56.000Z","uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f09cb31e98b9eb1e550815049d2bcdbf759fd5b","tid":370913,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的,小弟一早應承左同屋企人(老豆老母同我,一家三口)去個旅行,仲攞左五日大假TIM~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁兩老就話想去芭提雅，我未去過就諗住都OK LA。<br />\n<br />\n點知上網一search,好似普遍都話五日芭提雅太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔知咁多巴打係咪咁諗? <br />\n<br />\n我地budget就預五至六千一個人LA，大家覺得點?行程方面有無咩必去必玩?<br />\n<br />\n麻煩咁多位巴打俾D意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb9188833da12f36a9793e553158cbd59d7fec0","tid":370913,"uid":91362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"點解唔去埋曼谷？"},{"pid":"232ee45a993b62f353f60badab67a6e36f0af833","tid":370913,"uid":64835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"頂盡3日係芭堤雅都夠哂數，其餘日數不如上返去曼谷shopping"},{"pid":"a61ed225af5623e672e96d358c72624c56f5aefa","tid":370913,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔去埋曼谷？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆又話唔駛去埋曼谷,話芭提雅大把野玩,HEA下玩下就OK,但上網睇又好似係另一回事。巴打你點睇?依家我地未BOOK野,仲返到轉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863e34e77c6d4367c6fb92e8378fbae0e4ba59cf","tid":370913,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"曼谷芭提雅搭巴士單程多數3個鐘左右，2老未必接受到<br />\n佢地都話hea下咁就唔好搞咁多，到時佢地唔玩又話攰"},{"pid":"8d2ef1aa702ac292255850ec36a0f129ed8e7ebd","tid":370913,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"凈係帶你老豆就有野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n芭達雅無野好玩 <br />\n講Night life 曼谷都有<br />\n講Shopping 曼谷更加完勝<br />\n講女... D女污穢到仆街 夜晚行轉市中心已經Feel到 根本唔岩親子遊"},{"pid":"ebab5eb34751113480fc20f484d30e126f5f8712","tid":370913,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"同埋pattaya都唔係幾安全 要留意下"},{"pid":"bb835a2986747cd654a9bf0e98e86fa35316ab0c","tid":370913,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頂盡3日係芭堤雅都夠哂數，其餘日數不如上返去曼谷shopping</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪試過咁玩?行程大約係點?"},{"pid":"1901f78762272b927075753075cca54e7c061f0c","tid":370913,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋pattaya都唔係幾安全 要留意下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係擔心LEE樣.......上網睇講到成個淫都咁..."},{"pid":"447c1b1b6e75bdcd3fb3bc9c86d319aa8e422855","tid":370913,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔去埋曼谷？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆又話唔駛去埋曼谷,話芭提雅大把野玩,HEA下玩下就OK,但上網睇又好似係另一回事。巴打你點睇?依家我地未BOOK野,仲返到轉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUncle <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd350e3c45133003cff489f15177fbdcecc412a","tid":370913,"uid":11418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:54:04.000Z","msg":"5日芭堤雅⋯太多啦。<br />\n真係純Hea架咋去到，所以果邊絕大部分都係外國人多。<br />\n去曬太陽坐係街邊飲下酒咁就一日。<br />\n<br />\n5-6千左右一個人既話絕對可以做富豪⋯<br />\n港幣10蚊左右先一碟飯⋯5-6千蚊完全係豪食！<br />\n<br />\n個人認為2日芭堤雅，3日曼谷啦。<br />\n<br />\n落機先係機場坐巴士去芭堤雅，再番曼谷玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9415a4c5c533ebbb03571ce8b1de700193bafc75","tid":370913,"uid":11418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋pattaya都唔係幾安全 要留意下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係擔心LEE樣.......上網睇講到成個淫都咁...</blockquote><br />\n講真睇下你點睇⋯<br />\n你唔專登去果啲地方既真係無咩野<br />\n<br />\n不過治安黎講個人認為曼谷好好多。<br />\n因為芭堤雅既人好多都知黎親既都係外國人⋯<br />\n好多時見你係旅客樣就屈多你小小⋯<br />\n<br />\n相反番落曼谷，雖然都係旅客多，但屈錢情況小好多"},{"pid":"0a010e104c0f0aa22f27d63f7a7b44426d69971e","tid":370913,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:35:18.000Z","msg":"Book間高級酒店俾佢地渡下假算啦，最緊要有車接送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc28897a486dfbc66ac21550f489e639dbb7fb79","tid":370913,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"五日pattaya 唔係玩唔到 但你預咗要hea 玩<br />\n五日你可能咁樣玩啦 2日去koh larn 住下玩下水上活動訓下沙灘<br />\n一日去動物園加食嘢做spa<br />\n一日市中心shopping 食嘢做 下massage<br />\n仲有一日你另外睇下有咩想做 夾得啱night market 啲時間可以去行埋"},{"pid":"28b42be23684ce4e7307d948c1d5ab806c4dd27d","tid":370913,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"芭提雅無咩好玩"},{"pid":"71c56a122aabb951a77151aa12337e07b83ae09f","tid":370913,"uid":41007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"5日華欣仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}